  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>basmati</strong>&nbsp;<strong>rice</strong>, 400ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml]</span>&nbsp;<strong>water</strong> and a very large pinch&nbsp;of both <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> sugar</strong> to a pot (with a lid) and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and stir vigorously for 1 min, before covering for 15-20 min or until most of the water is absorbed, stirring occasionally&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once&nbsp;the rice is cooked, set aside and keep covered until serving&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>basa fillets</strong> in half lengthways and cut each half into bite-sized pieces&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a large mixing bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> fish pieces</strong> and coat them in the breadcrumbs to make <strong>fish nuggets</strong> (press the breadcrumbs onto the fish with clean hands)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>ginger</strong> (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and chop (or grate) finely</p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>ginger</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>sesame oil</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy), half of the <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and&nbsp;1 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tsp]</span><strong>&nbsp;sugar&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix well &ndash;<strong>&nbsp;</strong>this is your <strong>Asian dipping sauce&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;hot, add the <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> and cook for 4 min or until the skin starts to blacken slightly</p>\r\n<p>Transfer the <strong>charred</strong> <strong>sugar snaps</strong> to a bowl and cover to keep warm</p>\r\n<p>Reserve the pan for the next step</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium heat with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the breaded <strong>fish nuggets</strong> and cook on both sides for 1 min or until crispy and golden</p>\r\n<p>Transfer the cooked <strong>nuggets</strong> to a plate and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tip:&nbsp;cook in batches if needed</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/400.-400_.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
